  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要梳理一下物流系统的模块依赖关系。核心场景是车队管理、库存水位和配送路线这三个业务域，我想用类图来表达它们之间的调用和依赖。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_FleetManagement",
        "Logistics_StockLevel",
        "Logistics_DeliveryRoute"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，三个业务域。那具体有哪些实现层的东西？比如是CLI工具、桌面应用还是API服务？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CustomCli",
        "CustomApp",
        "CustomApi"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，正好对应五种形态：CustomCli是命令行工具，CustomApp是桌面应用，CustomApi是对外暴露的接口，CustomSdk是开发工具包，CustomLib是基础库。CLI和App都专注各自业务，CLI管车队，App管库存。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CustomCli",
        "CustomApp",
        "CustomApi",
        "CustomSdk",
        "CustomLib"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：CustomCli绑定Logistics_FleetManagement，CustomApp绑定Logistics_StockLevel，CustomApi绑定Logistics_DeliveryRoute。那Sdk和Lib呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CustomCli",
        "CustomApp",
        "CustomApi",
        "CustomSdk",
        "CustomLib"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Sdk比较特殊，它同时服务车队管理场景；Lib则支撑配送路线。依赖关系上，CLI和App都通过using关系去依赖Sdk和Lib，Sdk再依赖Lib。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CustomCli",
        "CustomSdk",
        "CustomLib",
        "CustomApp"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把using关系画出来：CustomCli指向Lib和Sdk，CustomApp指向Sdk，Sdk指向Lib。方向都是从使用者指向被依赖方。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CustomCli",
        "CustomLib",
        "CustomSdk",
        "CustomApp"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Sdk和Api之间还有关键的通信链路。Sdk发起bRequest消息给Api，业务上下文是车队管理；然后Api返回bResponse消息，带的是库存水位的数据。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CustomSdk",
        "CustomApi",
        "bRequest",
        "bResponse",
        "Logistics_FleetManagement",
        "Logistics_StockLevel"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "这里消息方向需要确认：bRequest是Sdk发给Api，所以是Sdk指向Api？bResponse是Api回给Sdk，所以是Api指向Sdk？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CustomSdk",
        "CustomApi",
        "bRequest",
